| [[电容|电容]]([[倒数|倒数]]) 
<math>\frac{1}{C}=\frac{\mathrm{d}U}{\mathrm{d}q}=\frac{\mathrm{d}\dot \Phi}{\mathrm{d}q}</math>
| [[电阻|电阻率]]
<math>R=\frac{\mathrm{d}U}{\mathrm{d}I}=\frac{\mathrm{d}\dot \Phi}{\mathrm{d}\dot{q}}</math>
