| [[电感|电感]]
<math>L=\frac{\mathrm{d}\Phi}{\mathrm{d}I}=\frac{\mathrm{d}\Phi}{\mathrm{d}\dot{q}}</math>
|}

== 实现 ==
[[Intel|Intel]]與[[Micron|Micron]]聯合研發的[[3D_XPoint|3D XPoint]]。（Intel表示所用并不是ReRAM，根据推断，为相变存储器的可能性更大，此条消息存疑。）廠商表示，此技術的密度是[[DRAM|DRAM]]的十倍、速度是[[NAND|NAND]]的千倍、寫入次數為10,000,000次。

== 潜在应用 ==
{{link-en|理查德·斯坦利·威廉姆斯|Richard Stanley Williams|威廉姆斯}}的固態的憶阻器可以組合成所謂{{link-en|交叉開關鎖存器|Crossbar latch}}的設備，這可能會取代[[晶體管|晶體管]]建造未來的[[电脑|电脑]]，佔用面積小得多。

== 種類 ==
=== 電化電池 ===
憶阻器具有[[電化電池|電化電池]]表現的特徵。<ref>{{Cite book en|author=Chen W-K|title=The Circuits and Filters Handbook|edition=2nd ed|publisher=CRC Press 2003|id=ISBN 0-8493-0912-3|chapter=Circuit Elements, Modeling, and Equation Formulation}}</ref>

=== 固態 ===
2007年[[惠普公司|惠普公司]]資訊與量子系統實驗室的研究人員在{{link-en|理查德·斯坦利·威廉姆斯|Richard Stanley Williams}}的領導下成功研製了固態的憶阻器<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/7080772.stm|title=Getting More from Moore's Law|last=Fildes|first=Jonathan|publisher=BBC|date=2007-11-13|accessdate=2008-04-30|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220122539/https://secure-uk.imrworldwide.com/v51.js|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ieee-or.org/beeep/2007/sep/beeep_sep07.pdf|format=PDF|title=Bulletin for Electrical and Electronic Engineers of Oregon|publisher=Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers|date=Sept 2007|accessdate=2008-04-30|archive-date=2008-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080530002152/http://www.ieee-or.org/beeep/2007/sep/beeep_sep07.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.hpl.hp.com/about/bios/stanwilliams.html| title = R. Stanley Williams, HP biography| access-date = 2008-05-02| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080513192702/http://www.hpl.hp.com/about/bios/stanwilliams.html| archive-date = 2008-05-13| dead-url = yes}}</ref>－它是由一片雙層的二氧化鈦薄膜所形成，當電流通過時，其電阻值就會改變。固態的憶阻器的製造需要涉及物料的納米技術。這個憶阻器並不像其理論般涉及[[磁通量|磁通量]]，或如[[電容器|電容器]]般儲存[[電荷|電荷]]，而是以[[化學|化學]]技術來達至[[電阻|電阻]]隨[[電流|電流]]歷史改變的性質。

不過，[[三星集團|三星集團]]卻有一項正申請專利的憶阻器，採用了類似惠普公司的技術。故此誰是憶阻器的創始人則有待澄清。<ref>[http://www.google.com/patents?id=hIKiAAAAEBAJ&dq=11655193, US Patent Application 11/655,193]{{Dead link}}</ref>

目前(2008)[[惠普公司|惠普公司]]是以兩層二氧化鈦薄膜來製作憶阻器元件<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.informationweek.com/news/hardware/processors/showArticle.jhtml?articleID=207403582 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2008-05-02 |archive-date=2010-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100627030009/http://www.informationweek.com/news/hardware/processors/showArticle.jhtml?articleID=207403582 |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，其中一層摻雜。<ref name="spectrum.ieee.org">{{cite web |url=http://www.spectrum.ieee.org/may08/6207 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080511231202/http://www.spectrum.ieee.org/may08/6207 |archivedate=2008-05-11 }}</ref>

== 可能應用 ==
其元件特性，適合模擬神經元突觸的部份運作，使得電腦神經網路製作上更能接近人腦。<ref name="spectrum.ieee.org"/>

威廉姆斯的固態憶阻器可以組合成晶體管，儘管小得多。They can also be fashioned into [[non-volatile_memory|non-volatile]] solid-state memory, which would allow greater data density than hard drives with access times potentially similar to [[Dynamic_random_access_memory|DRAM]], replacing both components.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.news.com/8301-10784_3-9932054-7.html|title=HP makes memory from a once theoretical circuit|last=Kanellos|first=Michael|publisher=CNET News.com|date=2008-04-30|accessdate=2008-04-30|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220122540/https://www.cnet.com/news/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
HP has reported that its version of the memristor is about 10 times slower than DRAM [http://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/01/technology/01chip.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/01/technology/01chip.html |date=20210220122537 }}.

